  "title": "BEAUTICIAN",
  "description": "<p>The job scope of a beautician is diverse and the tasks associated with the role of a beautician:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Client Consultation: </strong>Conducting thorough consultations with clients to understand their beauty goals, preferences, and any specific concerns or requirements.</li>\n  <li><strong>Skin Care: </strong>Providing facial treatments, including cleansing, exfoliation, masks, and moisturizing, to improve the health and appearance of the skin.</li>\n  <li><strong>Makeup Application: </strong>Applying makeup for various occasions, such as weddings, special events, or everyday wear, based on the client's requests.</li>\n  <li><strong>Massage Therapy: </strong>Providing massage and relaxation treatments to promote physical and mental well-being.</li>\n  <li><strong>Product Knowledge: </strong>Staying updated on beauty and skincare products, and recommending suitable products for clients to use at home.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Overall, a beautician's job is to help clients look and feel their best by offering a variety of beauty and grooming services while maintaining professionalism and a focus on customer satisfaction.</p>",
